{"tid":1004101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DJ Soda 榮獲「2018 年亞洲百大女 DJ 」第一名！","createTime":"2019-02-01T07:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T16:51:48.000Z","uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"056ccd913e5f901fdbfae256a538072b93abcd2f","tid":1004101,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T07:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://youtu.be/neGmbko585s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FneGmbko585s&h=6ed6d118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n說到 DJ 界的女神，大家第一時間肯定都會想到天使臉孔魔鬼身材的 DJ Soda ，擁有極高人氣的她，不僅是世界各大音樂 Party 指定邀請的 DJ ，也是眾所皆知的「女鞋頭」任何你想得到的限量球鞋、潮流單品她都有！不過人紅是非多，網路上總有些質疑她實力的聲音，日前《 DJane Mag》公佈了「2018 年亞洲百大女 DJ 」排行榜 DJ Soda 榮獲榜首之位！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/86281/5c2c68ae464a7.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F86281%2F5c2c68ae464a7.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=49ab8384&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/86281/5c2c68ae569ae.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F86281%2F5c2c68ae569ae.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=fc3623c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/86281/5c2c68ae57e93.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F86281%2F5c2c68ae57e93.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=f29cf796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以上是日前《 DJane Mag》公佈「2018 年亞洲百大女 DJ 」的榜單，可以看到 DJ Soda 在亞洲部分穩坐榜首的位置，緊追在後的是「台灣之光」DJ RAY RAY，不少人都看好明年 DJ RAY RAY 有望超越 DJ Soda！此外，DJ Soda 在全球 DJ 排行榜則是榮獲第 14 名的好成績，顯而易見，DJ Soda 除了擁有美麗的臉孔和火辣的身材外，她也相當有實力，並非是空有外表的美女。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/86281/5c2c68ba3ab26.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F86281%2F5c2c68ba3ab26.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=ede43842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/86281/5c2c68ba3d0fe.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F86281%2F5c2c68ba3d0fe.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=29c51997&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/86281/5c2c68ba3c0e5.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F86281%2F5c2c68ba3c0e5.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=62eeb7c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/86281/5c2c68ba478e6.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F86281%2F5c2c68ba478e6.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26q%3D75&h=cebf83f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://steamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/920292433854504346/9E4B35A13DD1A919233ECECE91AB77EC30CA44E3/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net%2Fugc%2F920292433854504346%2F9E4B35A13DD1A919233ECECE91AB77EC30CA44E3%2F&h=55d536b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ncache.ilbe.com/files/attach/new/20190108/2050903624/126567464/10952481889/7adaa6ed8336102c702942582a84e9c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fncache.ilbe.com%2Ffiles%2Fattach%2Fnew%2F20190108%2F2050903624%2F126567464%2F10952481889%2F7adaa6ed8336102c702942582a84e9c3.jpg&h=b03e59b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.qunba.com/2fc1549a0e29484a93be9363752ab6be.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.qunba.com%2F2fc1549a0e29484a93be9363752ab6be.png&h=60d06ede&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.juksy.com/archives/85679?atl=1&amp;gp=5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r